## Configuration examples

### Minimal production values

```yaml
database:
  postgres:
    bundled:
      enabled: false
    url: "postgres://agentregistry:changeme@pg.example.com:5432/agentregistry?sslmode=require"

config:
  existingSecret: "agentregistry-secrets"

resources:
  requests:
    cpu: 250m
    memory: 256Mi
  limits:
    cpu: 500m
    memory: 512Mi
```

### Production with connection string from a mounted file

```yaml
database:
  postgres:
    bundled:
      enabled: false
    urlFile: "/etc/secrets/db-url"

config:
  existingSecret: "agentregistry-secrets"
```

### Namespace-scoped RBAC

```yaml
rbac:
  watchedNamespaces:
    - first-app-ns
    - second-app-ns
```

